.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, hiking, rock-climbing, reading, collecting
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, poppy, marigold, iris, sunflower
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, social-worker, engineer, paramedic, bartender
House: futuristic, art-deco, wooden, tower, cape-cod
5 different games are played: chess, canasta, backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg

1. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is skydiving
2. the person who growspoppy is the person playing chess
3. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is hiking
4. the person who growsmarigold is the art-deco house
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing
6. the dressmaker is the person playing mah-jongg
7. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is reading
8. the wooden house is in the middle
9. the person who growsiris is on the far left
10. the engineer is on the left or right of the person playing canasta
11. the social-worker is to the left or right of the person playing snooker
12. the paramedic is the tower house
13. the person who growssunflower is the bartender
14. the person who growsiris is to the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting

.:: Answer ::.
